caller_intent: The caller (Brad) is seeking clarification on whether his existing liability insurance policy can be used for a Carvana car purchase he is paying for in full, and he offers to provide documentation for verification.
resolution_steps: Agent acknowledges the caller's request and confirms they will email insurance ID cards and coverage documentation.
Agent requests the caller to provide the VIN number of the vehicle once available.
knowledge_required: Understanding of insurance policy portability for vehicle purchases
Carvana's insurance requirements for full-payment buyers
summary: Brad inquires about using his existing liability insurance for a Carvana purchase. The agent agrees to send verification documents and requests the VIN number for processing. The caller commits to providing the VIN when available.
